Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小桃  爺爺  那我就走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.15,0:00:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  Summer School要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出門咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.41,0:00:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們也開始作戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶  爺爺  真的要做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出發吧  小桃隊員
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:20.99,Disp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,289)\fad(500,0)}式根島
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（歡迎來到式根島）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到咯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來到式根島  發現海的顏色都不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟距離大島有50公里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是天氣這麼好真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全員  朝著目標的旅館出發
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:02:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大海好漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}要是買了新泳衣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一色同學  二葉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三枝同學  四宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們把Operation Key都交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全員的鑰匙都由我來保管
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們的鑰匙與世界的命運息息相關
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在海裡弄掉了就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水羽老師說的很對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在Summer School結束前我會統一保管
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  你們可以出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們出發啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Valkyria-1呼叫WildVizell
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是Valkyria-1
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WildVizell請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WildVizell呼叫Valkyria-1　敏感度良好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報告  按照預定回收了全員的Operation Key
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼現在開始作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個  一色博士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些真的是為了她們好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次的Summer School
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是強化小茜她們友情力量的千載良機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老夫的特訓計劃是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特訓計劃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  向日葵你的泳衣好可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常合身哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看  跟我說的一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒  什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是之前兩人去買的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟若葉一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她說沒有泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也想過借我的給她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實若葉的泳衣的話  裝不下向日葵的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔  軟軟彈彈的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說…小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜！
